 />\n搵定幾個朋友/屋企人望實自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fbafa4561dba63399a5c928eee0c8ec96761375","tid":311374,"uid":22789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一係預約政府普通科門診 叫醫生俾封轉介信你去醫院排精神科 有自殺念頭個期可能都會俾早少少你 門診醫生會睇情況開住藥先 但始終人人情況不同 未必一定係咁<br />\n<br />\n如果你當刻情緒好差 頂唔順 就去急症再轉介<br />\n<br />\n有錢嘅就睇私家 不過好貴<br />\n<br />\n另外可搵社工求助<br />\n<br />\n樓主 最近係咪有事情困擾緊你？關於邊方面？<br />\n<br />\n有d較平的轉導服務都可以考慮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你呀<br />\n咁我等多陣先醫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想自殺但又等多陣先醫？"},{"pid":"dae45a826478949b6573e9a961bfbdf6248076e9","tid":311374,"uid":75993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去睇家庭醫生同佢講你情況 <br />\n叫佢寫張referral 畀你 <br />\n然後就可以拎去你住嗰區既精神科門診<br />\n畀護士同你做分流見醫生<br />\n據我所知正常無得即日睇架 <br />\n頂住啊巴打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩係家庭醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我應該無啲咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去附近政府門診或者私家診所<br />\n可以寫referral畀你去精神科門診<br />\n<br />\n私人執業嘅精神科醫生可以睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.seedoctor.com.hk/psychiatry-specialty-doctor.asp?class_list_id=34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seedoctor.com.hk%2Fpsychiatry-specialty-doctor.asp%3Fclass_list_id%3D34&d=r624e6JfBadnJJUekWgyGAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=f4c9a137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.seedoctor.com.hk/psychiatry-specialty-doctor.asp?class_list_id=34</a>"},{"pid":"9f393a92a0e6204fd729550c64853a3343c361b8","tid":311374,"uid":22311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:42:39.000Z","msg":"上面點解話愈食愈差？<br />\n應該話睇醫生唔係完全靠佢，唔係傷風感冒<br />\n藥要食，心態要調節，運動要做<br />\n轉介信可以睇政府普通科又或者普通街邊既私家醫生"},{"pid":"cc861549939b74a337324156f418eb5e8526ef84","tid":311374,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc